{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.280", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Zuh\u00f6rerinnen und Zuh\u00f6rer! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.281", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.281", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.282", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.282", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe am Dienstag erfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Antrag nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.240", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie vorgesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.241", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Freitag behandelt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.241", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.600", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern heute."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.080", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestern Morgen hatte ich ihn immer noch nicht vorliegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.081", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich geh\u00f6re zu denen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.082", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.082", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.083", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man sollte sich langfristig vorbereiten k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.083", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.084", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allen Dingen auf anscheinend wichtige Themen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.084", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.085", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die hier zur Hauptsendezeit debattiert werden sollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.085", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.086", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe dann den Antrag Mittwochmittag bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.086", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.087", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe gedacht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.087", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.088", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich werde es schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.088", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.089", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mich damit zu besch\u00e4ftigen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.089", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.090", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist d\u00fcrftige zwei Seiten lang und kam mir vom Inhalt her sehr bekannt vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.090", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.091", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hei\u00dft zwar nicht \u201eSteuermehrbelastung durch kalte Progression\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.091", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.092", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern \u201eAbschaffung der kalten Progression als heimliche Steuererh\u00f6hung bei der Einkommensteuer\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.092", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.093", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da habe ich mir gedacht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.093", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.094", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Titel kennst du irgendwo her.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.094", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.095", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.095", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.096", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich kannte ihn\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.096", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von einer Ver\u00f6ffentlichung des ifo-Instituts aus dem Jahr\u00a02016. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider sind die abgeschriebenen S\u00e4tze nicht gekennzeichnet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welchen Grund das hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich fand das Ganze doch sehr d\u00fcnn und einfach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allen Dingen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.840", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben die Untersuchung nicht grunds\u00e4tzlich wiedergegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nur Teile davon. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das verf\u00e4lscht ein bisschen das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was der Urheber mitteilen wollte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber gehen wir auf die Inhalte ein; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.600", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es gibt immer wieder den Vorwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.600", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir w\u00fcrden die AfD-Antr\u00e4ge nicht gezielt behandeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00f6chte ich jetzt tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.680", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.681", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.681", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.682", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine Zwischenfragen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.682", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht sollte ich aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Sie vielleicht Fragen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.720", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vorher noch etwas erkl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.721", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir nehmen das Wort \u201eSteuerprogression\u201c immer in den Mund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.721", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber was bedeutet es eigentlich? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.200", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben eine Steuerkurve, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.201", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Prinzip bedeutet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.201", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.202", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je mehr man verdient, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.202", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "desto h\u00f6her ist der Steuersatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.160", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den man zahlt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist von uns so gewollt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es wurde irgendwann einmal so beschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.000", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man h\u00e4tte es auch anders regeln k\u00f6nnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gab Parteien hier im Bundestag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.400", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gesagt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie k\u00f6nnten sich vorstellen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "25\u00a0Prozent \u00fcber alles. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch da w\u00fcrde die Steuersumme mit zunehmendem Einkommen steigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.080", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir von der SPD haben als Mantra \u201eStarke Schultern sollen mehr tragen\u201c."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.081", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen finden wir es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn bei zunehmendem Einkommen auch der Steuersatz steigt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Problematisch wird es erst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir eine hohe Inflationsrate bekommen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn dann wird das Geld weniger wert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ich auf dem Papier mehr verdiene und mehr Steuern zahle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "habe ich trotzdem weniger Kaufkraft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.440", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Effekt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.680", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der theoretisch eintreten kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist in den letzten Jahren aber nicht vorgekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe Daten des Statistischen Bundesamtes mitgebracht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.441", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich nenne immer meine Quellen\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.441", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.240", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Inflationsrate der letzten Jahre lag unter 2\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.160", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Ihrem Antrag hei\u00dft es\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das stimmt auch\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Draghi 2\u00a0Prozent anstrebt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.920", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die wurden aber in den letzten Jahren nicht erreicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.640", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen hatten wir auch nicht den Effekt der kalten Progression bei uns."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.160", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir aber in den letzten Jahren gemacht haben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben beschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.201", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ganze Entwicklung im Blick zu behalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.201", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.202", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und haben deswegen das BMF beauftragt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.202", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.203", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle zwei Jahre einen Bericht zur Entwicklung der kalten Progression vorzulegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.203", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.204", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die auch regelm\u00e4\u00dfig tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.204", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.205", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der letzte Bericht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.205", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.280", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der zweite Steuerprogressionsbericht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist vom November\u00a02016. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.321", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darin hei\u00dft es sinngem\u00e4\u00df: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.321", 
   "children": [], 
